<h3>The Freelancer Middle Ground</h3>
<p>Some businesses hire freelance writers instead of agencies. Freelancers charge $80 to $250 per article for SEO blog content. 30 articles per month from freelancers costs $2,400 to $7,500. You also spend 5 to 10 hours per month managing them. Assigning topics. Reviewing drafts. Requesting revisions. Publishing final versions.</p>
<p>Freelancers offer better per-article economics than agencies but still require significant management time. And finding reliable freelancers who understand <a href="/blog/seo-content-writing/">SEO content writing</a> takes trial and error. Most businesses cycle through 3 to 5 freelancers before finding one who produces consistently.</p>
